text: SUPERIOR luxury resort living on a double cul-de-sac street within the gated & guarded subdivision of Granada in Westlake. Refined, turn key, dialed in technology that feels like magic-- Control 4 system ($125k) controls music, lights, pool & security & 11 televisions that will convey! The open kitchen is a culinary space that inspires: Wolf stove, Sub Zero + wine tower in main kitchen & secondary Sub Zero in discreet butler's pantry complete with Wolf steam oven, second dishwasher & third sink! Focal piece with Boos block style wooded island that is special. An outdoor vibe like none other with: $300k worth of mature landscaping, spa, pool with tanning ledges, two custom waterfalls & fire pit. Outdoor entertaining & cooking: Wolf grill, Green Egg, expansive dining & seating areas footsteps from the pool. Enter the residence through a tranquil courtyard & experience a waterfall, travertine seating area, turf and oversized metal pivot front door. Elegance at every turn: wide plank wood floors throughout living areas and bedrooms, three fireplaces, wet bar with ice, refrigeration & bar seating, primary bath with dual private water closets, refrigerator drawers & in-suite washer & dryer in one of the separate closets. Study & exercise rooms are on a private wing-- exercise room could easily be second office. Private tucked away guest suite enjoys double door view of the courtyard. Every finish, every texture, every corner speaks of thoughtful luxury. A PentaVia Custom Home home offering an opportunity to move in and start enjoying every luxury upgrade for comfort and innovation. Pool bath off back game room, outdoor shower & lighting rods too. Transitional, Modern & Mediterranean buyers will love this exciting but functional floorplan. Private lot, 4 car garage (gated) & circle drive. Check out the school possibilities with this prestigious address. Truly a better value than new construction options.
